. Dalton is the neighbor of the young and promising actress and model Sharon Tate, who has just married the prestigious Polish director Roman Polanski…","genre_ids":[35,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.721,"vote_count":14579,"poster_path":"/8j58iEBw9pOXFD2L0nt0ZXeHviB.jpg","release_date":"2019-07-24","vote_average":7.423,"backdrop_path":"/kKTPv9LKKs5L3oO1y5FNObxAPWI.jpg","original_title":"Once Upon a Time... in Hollywood","original_language":"en"},{"id":297222,"adult":false,"title":"PK","video":false,"overview":"A stranger in the city asks questions no one has asked before. Known only by his initials, the man's innocent questions and childlike curiosity take him on a journey of love, laughter and letting go.","genre_ids":[35,18,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.4022,"vote_count":1122,"poster_path":"/z2x2Y4tncefsIU7h82gmUM5vnBJ.jpg","release_date":"2014-12-18","vote_average":7.698,"backdrop_path":"/gxfvtq5eYiClS2X7hxAAPBNrbWA.jpg","original_title":"पीके","original_language":"hi"},{"id":597,"adult":false,"title":"Titanic","video":false,"overview":"101-year-old Rose DeWitt Bukater tells the story of her life aboard the Titanic, 84 years later. A young Rose boards the ship with her mother and fiancé. Meanwhile, Jack Dawson and Fabrizio De Rossi win third-class tickets aboard the ship. Rose tells the whole story from Titanic's departure through to its death—on its first and last voyage—on April 15, 1912.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":28.4976,"vote_count":26827,"poster_path":"/9xjZS2rlVxm8SFx8kPC3aIGCOYQ.jpg","release_date":"1997-12-18","vote_average":7.903,"backdrop_path":"/xnHVX37XZEp33hhCbYlQFq7ux1J.jpg","original_title":"Titanic","original_language":"en"},{"id":264660,"adult":false,"title":"Ex Machina","video":false,"overview":"Caleb, a coder at the world's largest internet company, wins a competition to spend a week at a private mountain retreat belonging to Nathan, the reclusive CEO of the company. But when Caleb arrives at the remote location he finds that he will have to participate in a strange and fascinating experiment in which he must interact with the world's first true artificial intelligence, housed in the body of a beautiful robot girl.","genre_ids":[18,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.7588,"vote_count":14042,"poster_path":"/dmJW8IAKHKxFNiUnoDR7JfsK7Rp.jpg","release_date":"2015-01-21","vote_average":7.573,"backdrop_path":"/uqOuJ50EtTj7kkDIXP8LCg7G45D.jpg","original_title":"Ex Machina","original_language":"en"},{"id":13510,"adult":false,"title":"Eden Lake","video":false,"overview":"When a young couple goes to a remote wooded lake for a romantic getaway, their quiet weekend is shattered by an aggressive group of local kids. Rowdiness quickly turns to rage as the teens terrorize the couple in unimaginable ways, and a weekend outing becomes a bloody battle for survival.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.608,"vote_count":2024,"poster_path":"/tOg6ElTe1mJwaCFN0172U4oso22.jpg","release_date":"2008-09-12","vote_average":6.832,"backdrop_path":"/s9v1QZMVhwShQ7415jPhtfqzyjG.jpg","original_title":"Eden Lake","original_language":"en"},{"id":475557,"adult":false,"title":"Joker","video":false,"overview":"During the 1980s, a failed stand-up comedian is driven insane and turns to a life of crime and chaos in Gotham City while becoming an infamous psychopathic crime figure.","genre_ids":[80,53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":18.0422,"vote_count":27338,"poster_path":"/udDclJoHjfjb8Ekgsd4FDteOkCU.jpg","release_date":"2019-10-01","vote_average":8.128,"backdrop_path":"/hO7KbdvGOtDdeg0W4Y5nKEHeDDh.jpg","original_title":"Joker","original_language":"en"},{"id":791373,"adult":false,"title":"Zack Snyder's Justice League","video":false,"overview":"Determined to ensure Superman's ultimate sacrifice was not in vain, Bruce Wayne aligns forces with Diana Prince with plans to recruit a team of metahumans to protect the world from an approaching threat of catastrophic proportions.","genre_ids":[28,12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":9.4916,"vote_count":10644,"poster_path":"/tnAuB8q5vv7Ax9UAEje5Xi4BXik.jpg","release_date":"2021-03-18","vote_average":8.096,"backdrop_path":"/13Nz8EchKRdCgJcKdEoJAnpiVn2.jpg","original_title":"Zack Snyder's Justice League","original_language":"en"},{"id":105,"adult":false,"title":"Back to the Future","video":false,"overview":"Eighties teenager Marty McFly is accidentally sent back in time to 1955, inadvertently disrupting his parents' first meeting and attracting his mother's romantic interest. Marty must repair the damage to history by rekindling his parents' romance and - with the help of his eccentric inventor friend Doc Brown - return to 1985.","genre_ids":[12,35,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":18.5525,"vote_count":21421,"poster_path":"/vN5B5WgYscRGcQpVhHl6p9DDTP0.jpg","release_date":"1985-07-03","vote_average":8.324,"backdrop_path":"/qskzmLTbarKnXDbo2HRj4NJ3vcW.jpg","original_title":"Back to the Future","original_language":"en"},{"id":508442,"adult":false,"title":"Soul","video":false,"overview":"Joe Gardner is a middle school teacher with a love for jazz music. After a successful audition at the Half Note Club, he suddenly gets into an accident that separates his soul from his body and is transported to the You Seminar, a center in which souls develop and gain passions before being transported to a newborn child. Joe must enlist help from the other souls-in-training, like 22, a soul who has spent eons in the You Seminar, in order to get back to Earth.","genre_ids":[16,10751,35,14,18,10402],"media_type":"movie","popularity":12.2138,"vote_count":11204,"poster_path":"/6jmppcaubzLF8wkXM36ganVISCo.jpg","release_date":"2020-12-25","vote_average":8.097,"backdrop_path":"/rQaHA74pevnGsxcKGaoZVGWe9TC.jpg","original_title":"Soul","original_language":"en"},{"id":49046,"adult":false,"title":"All Quiet on the Western Front","video":false,"overview":"Paul Baumer and his friends Albert and Muller, egged on by romantic dreams of heroism, voluntarily enlist in the German army. Full of excitement and patriotic fervour, the boys enthusiastically march into a war they believe in. But once on the Western Front, they discover the soul-destroying horror of World War I.","genre_ids":[10752,36,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.1591,"vote_count":4528,"poster_path":"/2IRjbi9cADuDMKmHdLK7LaqQDKA.jpg","release_date":"2022-10-07","vote_average":7.721,"backdrop_path":"/zbOlpFM306PHE7EP1OELCH5qSmS.jpg","original_title":"Im Westen nichts Neues","original_language":"de"},{"id":545609,"adult":false,"title":"Extraction","video":false,"overview":"A hardened gun-for-hire's latest mission becomes a soul-searching race to survive when he's sent into Bangladesh to rescue a drug lord's kidnapped son.","genre_ids":[28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.7883,"vote_count":6492,"poster_path":"/nygOUcBKPHFTbxsYRFZVePqgPK6.jpg","release_date":"2020-04-23","vote_average":7.297,"backdrop_path":"/1R6cvRtZgsYCkh8UFuWFN33xBP4.jpg","original_title":"Extraction","original_language":"en"},{"id":11324,"adult":false,"title":"Shutter Island","video":false,"overview":"World War II soldier-turned-U.S. Marshal Teddy Daniels investigates the disappearance of a patient from a hospital for the criminally insane, but his efforts are compromised by troubling visions and a mysterious doctor.","genre_ids":[18,53,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.6244,"vote_count":25460,"poster_path":"/nrmXQ0zcZUL8jFLrakWc90IR8z9.jpg","release_date":"2010-02-14","vote_average":8.2,"backdrop_path":"/8xt8AMb1OKC63AdhNSaYBWxB4Iq.jpg","original_title":"Shutter Island","original_language":"en"},{"id":551332,"adult":false,"title":"The Two Popes","video":false,"overview":"Frustrated with the direction of the church, Cardinal Bergoglio requests permission to retire in 2012 from Pope Benedict. Instead, facing scandal and self-doubt, the introspective Pope Benedict summons his harshest critic and future successor to Rome to reveal a secret that would shake the foundations of the Catholic Church.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.406,"vote_count":3098,"poster_path":"/4d4mTSfDIFIbUbMLUfaKodvxYXA.jpg","release_date":"2019-11-27","vote_average":7.491,"backdrop_path":"/bOPessdyd0dChHy70FM8Om7CgDg.jpg","original_title":"The Two Popes","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":71,"adult":false,"title":"Billy Elliot","video":false,"overview":"County Durham, England, 1984. The miners' strike has started and the police have started coming up from Bethnal Green, starting a class war with the lower classes suffering. Caught in the middle of the conflict is 11-year old Billy Elliot, who, after leaving his boxing club for the day, stumbles upon a ballet class and finds out that he's naturally talented. He practices with his teacher Mrs. Wilkinson for an upcoming audition in Newcastle-upon Tyne for the royal Ballet school in London.","genre_ids":[18,35,10402],"popularity":2.8329,"vote_count":4027,"poster_path":"/nOr5diUZxphmAD3li9aiILyI28F.jpg","release_date":"2000-09-28","vote_average":7.593,"backdrop_path":"/mTsbahr4SLqgVZkKRN0O8t5iA9y.jpg","original_title":"Billy Elliot","original_language":"en"},{"id":99,"adult":false,"title":"All About My Mother","video":false,"overview":"Following the tragic death of her teenage son, Manuela travels from Madrid to Barcelona in an attempt to contact the long-estranged father the boy never knew. She reunites with an old friend, an outspoken transgender sex worker, and befriends a troubled actress and a pregnant, HIV-positive nun.","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":2.4504,"vote_count":2027,"poster_path":"/hjQhzhkGYXPNM96k0mOgob6HMmn.jpg","release_date":"1999-04-16","vote_average":7.628,"backdrop_path":"/tilClWjFZeUTGJu0pxgF72fvUmN.jpg","original_title":"Todo sobre mi madre","original_language":"es"},{"id":140,"adult":false,"title":"Bad Education","video":false,"overview":"When an old friend brings filmmaker Enrique Goded a semi-au