 Chris begins to confront waht he left in the city. Like the proud Datu with many wives, Chris has Denver, a bronze skinned lover in Manila, who is proud of his relationships. Denver lives with Chris in an apartment as partners yet he still goes into sexual and emotional relationships with other men. Ngapon's quest for freedom becomes Chris journey to a very sad dark past.  - Written by Anonymous","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.2309,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/oKRDC0ul0qXzaLBeis8k2aHSKTl.jpg","release_date":"2007-06-20","vote_average":4.1,"backdrop_path":"/tmULj2zOy644sKW4yayc1fqimYX.jpg","original_title":"Moreno","original_language":"tl"},{"id":159,"adult":false,"title":"Maybe... Maybe Not","video":false,"overview":"The heterosexual man Axel is thrown out of his girlfriends home for cheating and ends up moving in with a gay man. Axel learns the advantages of living with gay men even though they are attracted to him and when his girlfriend wants him back he must make a tough decision.","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":0.3921,"vote_count":117,"poster_path":"/2TcZBHcseRXLxNq2RXnKIsbKZwi.jpg","release_date":"1994-10-05","vote_average":6.218,"backdrop_path":"/cLOyix71NJwkfwt77bnmmy9ibJO.jpg","original_title":"Der bewegte Mann","original_language":"de"},{"id":854397,"adult":false,"title":"Light","video":false,"overview":"Haunted by trauma and trapped in sex work, Light meets Shuo, an undercover cop who offers him shelter. But healing isn’t easy—can Light choose a new path?","genre_ids":[10749,18,80],"popularity":0.4471,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/d8xahtp7qfMI5qA29ZeKIqnkHYN.jpg","release_date":"2021-08-13","vote_average":5.4,"backdrop_path":"/xUurlNwe3daHbkHzWd6E9mz9QfM.jpg","original_title":"小光","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1252745,"adult":false,"title":"Blue for a Boy","video":false,"overview":"A married woman discovers her husband is having an affair with a male prostitute and wants to meet the lover to get answers. However, her plans are interrupted when she gets a heart-stopping call from the hospital — her husband had a stroke and is lying unconscious. The wife and the lover — who fell in love with the husband — both rush to the hospital, and the remainder of the film highlights the dynamic of the two grappling with their situation as they both wait for the husband to recover in the ICU.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":0.3287,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/lHd3YgFQf2CvyDgeUVV2TgAxl3R.jpg","release_date":"2025-06-27","vote_average":7.5,"backdrop_path":"/k2IG59OuBGdCzSMQcfzFSnNMPZe.jpg","original_title":"Azul de niño","original_language":"es"},{"id":1252791,"adult":false,"title":"Loulou","video":false,"overview":"Loulou is 13 years old. He returns from his training and finds the house empty. He enters his parents’ bedroom and opens his mother’s cupboards...","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.6645,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/kzJMOl8OfRj6l7PNt7uutuPp85m.jpg","release_date":"2023-06-09","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/ggT2Uz4J0wBriCbHlnep6MFZW8d.jpg","original_title":"Loulou","original_language":"fr"},{"id":854586,"adult":false,"title":"Techno, Mama","video":false,"overview":"Nikita loves to listen to techno music and dreams to go to Berlin and visit the famous club “Berghain”. His mother Irena doesn’t know about his son’s dreams and soon enough their mutual expectations will clash.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.1551,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/pRa6CZYiQNWTotZyL3cKbGniu25.jpg","release_date":"2022-01-23","vote_average":4.25,"backdrop_path":"/2s91YApTaAJmEMMSeQQo6lYbE1i.jpg","original_title":"Techno, Mama","original_language":"lt"},{"id":1058689,"adult":false,"title":"My Animal","video":false,"overview":"Tormented by a hidden family curse, Heather lives in seclusion on the outskirts of a small town. When she falls for the rebellious Jonny, their connection threatens to unravel Heather's suppressed desires, tempting her to unleash the animal within.","genre_ids":[27,10749,14],"popularity":0.4832,"vote_count":28